# subscript(_:)

**Instance Subscript**

Accesses an element at an index.

## Declaration

```swift
subscript(position: Int) -> Any? { get set }
```

## Parameters

- **position**: A valid index in the column.

## Accessing Elements

- **subscript(_:)**: Accesses a contiguous subrange of the elements.

items.description: Accesses a contiguous subrange of the elements.
